---
title: Saucy Mexican Bean Enchiladas  with Charred Corn Salsa & Sour Cream
description: With beans, tortillas, plant-based cheese and charred yet sweet salsa, this Mexican favourite is colourful, delicious and a heap of
fun to make. Don’t forget to dollop on the sour cream to really get the fiesta going!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/65bc7b3b23af27a6dfb312c1-b398bff6.jpeg
